    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="69718-102">權限可以建立完全限制或完全不限制的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-102">Permissions can be created in either a totally restrictive or totally unrestrictive state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69718-103">完全不限制狀態可讓任何資源的存取權。完全不受限制的狀態可讓所有存取特定資源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-103">A totally restrictive state allows no access to resources; a totally unrestricted state allows all access to a particular resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69718-104">例如，檔案權限的建構函式無法建立物件，表示沒有存取權的任何檔案或所有檔案的所有存取。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-104">For example, the file permission constructor could create an object representing either no access to any files or all access to all files.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69718-105">每種類型的權限會清楚地定義狀態，或全部不可以表示的型別內的權限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-105">Each type of permission clearly defines extreme states representing either all or none of the permissions expressible within the type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="69718-106">因此，很可能在完全限制或無限制不知情的情況下的特定權限狀態; 建立泛型權限不過，可以只設定中繼狀態，根據特定的權限語意。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-106">Thus, it is possible to create a generic permission in a completely restricted or unrestricted state without knowledge of the particular permission; however, intermediate states can only be set according to the specific permission semantics.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69718-107">所有.NET Framework 中實作的程式碼存取權限都才能<xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>當做其建構函式的引數的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69718-107">All code access permissions implemented in the .NET Framework can take a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> value as an argument to their constructor.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
